sellerCard.description:
Hi Everyone

I'm Malix a seasoned web expert with a wealth of experience in crafting websites and developing web solutions My passion lies in web automation and the creation of custom webdriven Software as a Service (SaaS) applications.

Throughout my journey, I've mastered an array of programming languages and platforms including React Nodejs Angular Python Java and WordPress. Whether your goal is a dazzling website, streamlined web processes or tailored web solutions I'm here to deliver excellence.

Reach out to me Now and let's build something amazing together!

description.content:
Hello! I'm Malix, a web expert who for last 6 years focused solely on web. I do websites, web automation, SAAS or any time of web solutions. From initial prototyping/mockups to UI/UX Design then to development and then deploying it online. I handle everything related to Web.


Unlock a world of possibilities with my signature package, featuring:


  • Complimentary Consultation Session
  • Unlimited Revisions
  • Hosting
  • Seamless Mobile Responsive Designs
  • Support & Maintenance


What I offer:


  • Crafting Web-Driven SAAS Dashboards
  • Full-Stack Web Application Development
  • Tailored Website Customization
  • E-commerce Website Development
  • Expertise in Cloning Websites
  • Proficient Frontend and Backend Development
  • Specialization in React-based E-commerce Platforms
  • Building with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Tailwind
  • Crafting Engaging Landing Pages, Portfolios, and Business Websites
  • Seamless API Integrations
  • Rigorous Testing and Bug Resolution


My proficiency extends across various technologies, such as:


  • React.js
  • HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS
  • Angular
  • WordPress
  • JavaScript
  • MySQL
  • MongoDB
  • Node.js
  • Express.js


Shoot me a text and let's hop into a call to discuss and revolutionize your idea.
